Contextual Marketing: The New Wireless Killer App?

Wireless technologies that combine the benefits of the
physical and virtual worlds and empower mobile users will
prevail. The future of wireless for media delivery is up
for grabs, and countless start-ups know it. Bruno discusses
one such company's product.

http://clickz.com/article/cz.3912.html















